18.61	Hudson_Hawk	Hudson Hawk	Hudson Hawk is a 1991 American action comedy film directed by Michael Lehmann. Bruce Willis stars in the title role and also co-wrote the story. Danny Aiello, Andie MacDowell, James Coburn, David Caruso, Lorraine Toussaint, Frank Stallone, Sandra Bernhard, and Richard E. Grant are also featured.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/75/Hudson_hawk_ver2.jpg/215px-Hudson_hawk_ver2.jpg
